<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title || "Turtle Shelter Project" %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                <h1>TURTLE SHELTER PROJECT</h1>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#story">Jen's Story</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#sponsors">Thank You to Our Sponsors</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#help">How You Can Help</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay">
            <h2>Helping to save lives of people experiencing homelessness</h2>
            <h1>STARTS WITH YOU</h1>
            <a href="#help" class="btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main>
        <section id="about" class="about">
            <div class="content">
                <h2>What is a Turtle Shelter Vest?</h2>
                <p>A high-tech but simple solution to help save lives – a portable "shelter" you can carry with you, just like a turtle… and you can help!</p>
                <p>One winter when Jen was homeless, 7 of her friends froze to death. She found a solution: High-tech foam vests that are inexpensive, keep a person warm to 10 degrees below zero, and alleviate suffering.</p>
                <p><em>YOU</em> can request vests for your community – and you can make vests with your friends, business colleagues, church members, or club members too!</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="actions" class="actions">
            <div class="action-item">
                <h3>About</h3>
                <p>Learn Jen's story, from homelessness to saving lives, plus our mission, team, and all about the tech that makes our vests so special.</p>
                <a href="#about" class="link">Learn More →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-image">
                <img src="/images/turtle-logo.png" alt="Every Life Has Value Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="action-item">
                <h3>Take Action</h3>
                <p>Ready to take the next step? You can request vests, donate, make vests yourself, or organize an event!</p>
                <a href="#help" class="link">Find Out How →</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Turtle Shelter Project. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank" class="social-icon">
                <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com" target="_blank" class="social-icon">
                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com" target="_blank" class="social-icon">
                <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
            </a>
        </div>        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>
                TURTLE SHELTER PROJECT, PO BOX 382, KAYSVILLE, UT 84037 &nbsp;&nbsp; 
                801-872-3190 &nbsp;&nbsp; 
                <a href="mailto:turtleshelterproject@gmail.com">TURTLESHELTERPROJECT@GMAIL.COM</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
</body>
</html>
